      "Deadly Demise D3 , Deep Strike FACTION: Nurgle\u2019s Gift (Aura) Horrifying Visage: Each time this model ends a Charge move , select one enemy unit within Engagement Range of it. That unit must take a Battle-shock test , subtracting 1 from that test. Enfeebling Miasma (Aura): While an enemy unit (excluding MONSTERS and VEHICLES ) is within 6\" of this model, each time that unit is selected to Fall Back , models in that enemy unit must take Desperate Escape tests . When doing so, if that enemy unit is Battle-shocked , subtract 1 from each of those Desperate Escape tests."
